    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at this risk level per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 criterion is satisfied across all five COU operating points. The credibility assessment team accepted the CFD model as fit for the stated COU. Note: biological variability in donor red blood cell fragility affecting the hemolysis index validation result (VR-03) was acknowledged qualitatively by the team but was not captured in a structured uncertainty quantification record.",
